FBIS3-33913 "drnes022_a_94006" FBIS-NES-94-022 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Feb 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Security Services Confirm Killing of French Reporter LD0102153194 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 1 Feb 94 LD0102153194 Algiers Radio Algiers Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Once again, two more foreign reporters, working for ABC, the Australian Broadcasting Corporation, were the victims of an attack in the Casbah quarter of Algiers. A statement by the security services has disclosed that the two reporters were taken to the hospital where one of them, a French national, died of his wounds. The same source added that the other reporter, an Australian national, is in a critical condition.
